Meet Marcy! Marcy is a four month old Calico kitten who just arrived from Red Bluff, CA. She's looking for her new family! She has some anxiety about being left alone, so she'd prefer to be in a home where someone is home most of the day and where she'd have another cat-friendly cat to keep her company. Come meet this cutie when we open at noon tomorrow!

Midnight and Pluto are two very special pups. They have been with the @SunshineFoundationSTX since Hurricane Irma. They, along with their feline sister Lola, will finally be flying back to Florida to be reunited with their family. Pictured here, they are showing off their beautiful new coats after a spa day - they wanted to look extra nice to see their family again! 📷: @sunshinefoundationstx

AVAILABLE FOR ADOPTION!!! Meet Samson, a handsome 1 year old Lab/Hound mix. Samson is a very happy wiggly boy that is such a joy to be around. He was recently rescued from an area shelter and is adjusting well in his foster home. He is great with all dogs and is the “can’t we all just get along” type. He is eager to please and already knows sit. He is an affectionate boy that loves pets and kisses. He is housetrained and doing well with crate training. He will make a wonderful addition to any family. He is around 52lbs and will weigh around 58lbs. He is current on vaccines and will be neutered and microchipped on 1/31/18. We are currently accepting applications on Samson. Contact us today at adopt@carolinapaws.com to meet this very endearing boy. #Carolinapaws, #dog, #dogs, #adopt, #adoption, #rescue, #petfinder, #dogsofinstagram, #sweet, #charlotte, #lovedogs, #rescuedog, #cute, #rescuesrock, #rescuedogsofinstagram, #adorable, #secondchance, #northcarolina, #adoptlove, #loverescues, #saved #Waxhaw #clt #charlottenc #adoptdontshop #704
